TITLE: Querying Azure AD Group by Display Name
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to retrieve Azure AD group information using display name and security enabled filter. This is a common pattern for looking up existing security groups.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-azuread/blob/main/docs/data-sources/group.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
data "azuread_group" "example" {
  display_name     = "MyGroupName"
  security_enabled = true
}
```

