DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use "azuread_application_registration" and "azuread_application_redirect_uris" Terraform resources to define and assign multiple redirect URIs for different Azure AD app types (PublicClient, SPA, Web). Dependencies include the AzureAD Terraform provider and valid Azure credentials with specific API roles. Inputs: application_id as resource ID, redirect_uris as a list of URIs, and type specifying URI grouping. Outputs: Manages redirect URIs in Azure AD; resource is incompatible with azuread_application, and type changes force replacement.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-azuread/blob/main/docs/resources/application_redirect_uris.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
resource "azuread_application_registration" "example" {
  display_name = "example"
}

