TITLE: Listing HCL Operators and Delimiters
DESCRIPTION: Enumerates the character sequences recognized as operators, delimiters, and other special tokens within the HCL syntax. These symbols are fundamental building blocks for constructing HCL expressions and structures.
SOURCE: https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-azuread/blob/main/vendor/github.com/hashicorp/hcl/v2/hclsyntax/spec.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
+    &&   ==   <    :    {    [    (    ${
-    ||   !=   >    ?    }    ]    )    %{
*    !         <=        =         .
/              >=        =>        ,
%                                  ...
```

